      • CassandraDriver

        public CassandraDriver(String username,
                       String password,
                       String contactPoints,
                       int port,
                       String localDC,
                       String keyspace)
        Initializes the Driver
        Parameters:
        username - Name of User
        password - Password of user
        contactPoints - Comma separated list of contact points for Cassandra cluster. Order is ignored.
        port - Port Cassandra is listening on. Typically 9042
        localDC - Which dc to consider local
        keyspace - Default keyspace
